OL,3,CIce cream seller investigated over
OL,4,Cclaims van chimes are too loud
OL,6,FAn ice cream seller is being
OL,7,Finvestigated over claims his van's
OL,8,Fchimes are too loud.
OL,10,FEast Lindsey District Council notified
OL,11,FJamie Tomlinson, who runs Harrison's
OL,12,FIces, that someone had taken issue
OL,13,Fwith the music he plays on his rounds
OL,14,Fwhen he was in Louth, Lincolnshire,
OL,15,Flast month.
OL,17,FThe authority says it has a statutory
OL,18,Fduty to investigate all complaints,
OL,19,Falthough it has not installed any
OL,20,Fnoise-monitoring equipment as part of
OL,21,Fits enquiries.
