OL,3,CIce cream seller investigated over
OL,4,Cclaims van chimes are too loud
OL,6,FJamie described the claim as
OL,7,F"nonsense", insisting he adheres to
OL,8,Fall the relevant regulations on ice
OL,9,Fcream van chimes.
OL,11,FHe said: "We can only chime for 12
OL,12,Fseconds - you have to wait two minutes
OL,13,Fbefore you can go onto the next street
OL,14,Fto start chiming. The decibels for
OL,15,Finstance - ours is about 45. The
OL,16,Fhighest you can be is 80 decibels"
