OL,3,CIce cream seller investigated over
OL,4,Cclaims van chimes are too loud
OL,6,FAs well as guidance over the frequency
OL,7,Fand volume, there are laws governing
OL,8,Fice cream van chimes, including that
OL,9,Fthey can must be operated between the
OL,10,Fhours of noon and 7pm, and "as not to
OL,11,Fgive reasonable cause for annoyance to
OL,12,Fpersons in the vicinity."
