OL,3,CIce cream seller investigated over
OL,4,Cclaims van chimes are too loud
OL,6,FA spokesperson from East Lindsey
OL,7,FDistrict Council said: "The council
OL,8,Fdoes not have a choice in whether or
OL,9,Fnot to investigate. This is part of
OL,10,Four statutory duty to investigate
OL,11,Fpotential statutory nuisance under the
OL,12,FEnvironmental Protection Act 1990
OL,13,Fwhich state we must investigate all
OL,14,Fcomplaints we receive.
OL,16,F"Every year we receive and investigate
OL,17,Fin excess of 800 noise complaints
OL,18,Fabout a variety of issues ranging from
OL,19,Fdog barking to industrial noise."
